collectors.titleDetails: (5 total Queries, 5 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT o.id, o.code AS order_code, o.total_price, o.status, o.payment_image, o.address, u.username, CONCAT('[', GROUP_CONCAT( CONCAT( '{', '\"id\":', oi.product_id, ',', '\"quantity\":', oi.qty, ',', '\"price\":', oi.price, ',', '\"name\":\"', REPLACE(p.name, '"', '\\"'), '\",', '\"description\":\"', REPLACE(p.description, '"', '\\"'), '\"', '}' ) ), ']') AS products FROM orders o JOIN order_items oi ON oi.order_id = o.id JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.id JOIN users u ON o.user_id = u.id GROUP BY o.id

timelineData.name: Query
timelineData.query: SELECT o.id, o.code AS order_code, o.total_price, o.status, o.payment_image, o.address, u.username, CONCAT('[', GROUP_CONCAT( CONCAT( '{', '\"id\":', oi.product_id, ',', '\"quantity\":', oi.qty, ',', '\"price\":', oi.price, ',', '\"name\":\"', REPLACE(p.name, '"', '\\"'), '\",', '\"description\":\"', REPLACE(p.description, '"', '\\"'), '\"', '}' ) ), ']') AS products FROM orders o JOIN order_items oi ON oi.order_id = o.id JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.id JOIN users u ON o.user_id = u.id GROUP BY o.id
